{"tid":1860504,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手快樂","createTime":"2020-02-03T16:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T17:46:05.000Z","uid":324123,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"49f3fd806227dba92cab3666b344f60085574a8f","tid":1860504,"uid":324123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:30:48.000Z","msg":"今日正正係啱啱好7個月<br />\n最後都係敵唔過時間同考驗<br />\n同你一齊可以話係最開心<br />\n所有野一直都以為好美好<br />\n直到最近<br />\n我開始慢慢覺得你已經對我唔再感興趣<br />\n覺得同我一齊好悶 好唔開心<br />\n我已經諗盡辦法去挽救一段曾經好美好既關係<br />\n但係 我而家已經好攰 我好無助 我唔知可以點算<br />\n希望分開以後 你會揾到個你更鐘意 更優秀既女朋友<br />\n係我佩唔上你 你值得更好<br />\n有緣既話希望你會睇到我對你最後一段說話<br />\n7個月 再見。"},{"pid":"1adcf2b0a0be92a8373afa32cb3ea222edd37d25","tid":1860504,"uid":176472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:43:08.000Z","msg":"大家一齊喊下"},{"pid":"21dd0b7c61751dee58a15434be1a856ced4a567d","tid":1860504,"uid":324123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1adcf2b0a0be92a8373afa32cb3ea222edd37d25","tid":1860504,"uid":176472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:43:08.000Z","msg":"大家一齊喊下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:46:16.000Z","msg":"你又啱啱分手？"},{"pid":"c947f3ea93a6cced401181235e314d715be8aeba","tid":1860504,"uid":13405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:47:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d89e32f318cd5eaf40ac32618f19c82fc7ecc7","tid":1860504,"uid":324123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c947f3ea93a6cced401181235e314d715be8aeba","tid":1860504,"uid":13405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:47:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T16:48:14.000Z","msg":"唉 我都好撚認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b32e181e6db9f85ddfaaaa6d3969358f3de816","tid":1860504,"uid":4244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited